---
title: Easter Rosemary & Garlic Lamb with Chocolate Brownies for Dessert
description: Roast a tender and succulent lamb rump that's just right for a small gathering. With all the flavour of traditional roast lamb, plus
a decadent potato bake on the side, this dinner includes everything you need for a special occasion meal. And the best meals
end with a sweet treat, so we've included decadent chocolate brownies for dessert!
